Determined to go on,

00:58:31.195 --> 00:58:36.909 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Knowing that my God is always near—

00:58:36.909 --> 00:58:41.121 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith.

00:58:41.121 --> 00:58:48.045 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith, I can move a mountain.

00:58:48.045 --> 00:58:55.177 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith, my hope is sure.

00:58:55.177 --> 00:58:57.429 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Where would I be

00:58:57.429 --> 00:59:01.767 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Without the faith that helps me see

00:59:01.767 --> 00:59:10.359 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Beyond the trials I endure?

00:59:12.528 --> 00:59:19.326 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I see the wondrous future

00:59:19.326 --> 00:59:24.248 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
God has in store for me.

00:59:25.874 --> 00:59:29.044 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I need to be strong.

00:59:29.044 --> 00:59:32.214 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I know it won’t be long

00:59:32.214 --> 00:59:38.637 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Till Jehovah claims his victory.

00:59:38.637 --> 00:59:41.223 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith,

00:59:41.223 --> 00:59:45.561 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I see beyond the darkness.

