With Jehovah, I am strong,

00:59:56.530 --> 01:00:00.284 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Determined to go on,

01:00:00.284 --> 01:00:06.290 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Knowing that my God is always near—

01:00:09.626 --> 01:00:14.381 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With eyes of faith,

