With eyes of faith.

01:00:34.318 --> 01:00:38.197 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What a powerfully motivating video!

01:00:38.197 --> 01:00:41.950 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And we look forward to singing that song

01:00:41.950 --> 01:00:45.412 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to conclude our convention.

01:00:45.412 --> 01:00:47.748 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Dear brothers and sisters,

01:00:47.748 --> 01:00:49.750 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
faithful children,

01:00:49.750 --> 01:00:52.294 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
cherished interested ones,

01:00:52.294 --> 01:00:55.422 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
there’s no doubt that right now

01:00:55.422 --> 01:00:58.926 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we face powerful enemies.

01:00:58.926 --> 01:01:02.346 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
For one thing, we have a powerful enemy

01:01:02.346 --> 01:01:04.389 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
inside our bodies

01:01:04.389 --> 01:01:06.391 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—inherited sin.

01:01:06.391 --> 01:01:11.480 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It wages an intense war
against our desire to do what is right.

01:01:12.439 --> 01:01:16.443 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Secondly, we have the formidable foes:

01:01:16.443 --> 01:01:19.530 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Satan and his demons.

01:01:19.530 --> 01:01:23.116 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Satan is described as a devouring lion,

01:01:23.116 --> 01:01:25.118 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a cunning serpent,

01:01:25.118 --> 01:01:27.204 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a fierce dragon,

01:01:27.204 --> 01:01:29.206 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a sneaky birdcatcher,

01:01:29.206 --> 01:01:31.917 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and he’s given other evil descriptions.

01:01:31.917 --> 01:01:34.336 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Ephesians 6:12 says:

01:01:34.336 --> 01:01:38.840 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We have a struggle
[the footnote, literally “a wrestling”]

01:01:38.840 --> 01:01:43.845 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
. . . against the wicked spirit forces
in the heavenly places.”

01:01:43.845 --> 01:01:48.141 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And as mentioned in our publications,
there may be tens of thousands

01:01:48.141 --> 01:01:51.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of these powerful, evil spirit creatures

01:01:51.562 --> 01:01:53.564 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in the invisible realm

01:01:53.564 --> 01:01:57.901 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
waging war against us.

01:01:57.901 --> 01:02:02.406 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Thirdly, we have this wicked world
all around us

01:02:02.406 --> 01:02:05.158 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that is trying to assimilate us

01:02:05.158 --> 01:02:09.538 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
into joining them in ungodly conduct.

01:02:09.538 --> 01:02:11.707 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And looking at the ratio,

01:02:11.707 --> 01:02:15.961 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we as Jehovah’s people
are outnumbered by people of the world

01:02:15.961 --> 01:02:20.507 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
by about 900 to 1.

01:02:20.507 --> 01:02:25.304 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But despite the power
of those three great enemies,

01:02:25.304 --> 01:02:30.309 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
our faith—this product
of Jehovah’s invincible holy spirit—

01:02:31.059 --> 01:02:36.023 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
makes us stronger and stronger individually

01:02:36.023 --> 01:02:40.068 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
than all of those three enemies combined.

01:02:41.361 --> 01:02:43.405 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the near future,

01:02:43.405 --> 01:02:46.742 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
another powerful enemy will come against us.

01:02:46.742 --> 01:02:49.620 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This formidable foe

01:02:49.620 --> 01:02:54.625 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is a coalition of nations
called Gog in Ezekiel chapter 38.

01:02:54.625 --> 01:02:59.630 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And Ezekiel chapter 38 says
that Gog will come with “a great assembly,

01:02:59.630 --> 01:03:01.715 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a vast army.”

01:03:01.715 --> 01:03:04.301 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Like clouds covering the land,”

01:03:04.301 --> 01:03:07.971 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
they will come against God’s people.

01:03:07.971 --> 01:03:11.558 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, this could be
a very intimidating situation.

01:03:11.558 --> 01:03:13.560 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But dear brothers and sisters,

01:03:13.560 --> 01:03:18.565 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
your faith will make you stronger than Gog

01:03:18.565 --> 01:03:20.859 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and will keep you strong

01:03:20.859 --> 01:03:24.780 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
until Jehovah miraculously intervenes
at Armageddon.

01:03:24.780 --> 01:03:28.408 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And if you think about it,
Armageddon really is a rescue operation.

01:03:28.408 --> 01:03:30.410 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He will intervene,

01:03:30.410 --> 01:03:35.248 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and he will sweep attacking Gog away forever

01:03:35.248 --> 01:03:39.294 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with a “broom of annihilation.”

01:03:39.294 --> 01:03:43.632 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the past, faith has helped God’s people

01:03:43.632 --> 01:03:47.803 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to overcome the most powerful obstacles,

01:03:47.803 --> 01:03:50.764 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and that same product of holy spirit

01:03:50.764 --> 01:03:52.974 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
will help us do the same.

01:03:52.974 --> 01:03:57.270 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yes, throughout the centuries,
just like today,

01:03:57.270 --> 01:03:59.690 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
God’s servants, such as Daniel,

01:03:59.690 --> 01:04:02.776 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
have been made powerful,

01:04:02.776 --> 01:04:07.698 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
not by natural strength, but through faith.

01:04:07.698 --> 01:04:10.492 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So dear brothers and sisters,

01:04:10.492 --> 01:04:12.828 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
faithful children,

01:04:12.828 --> 01:04:15.372 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
cherished interested ones,

01:04:15.372 --> 01:04:17.874 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
pray earnestly for faith.

01:04:17.874 --> 01:04:21.253 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Put up a hard fight to maintain your faith.

01:04:21.253 --> 01:04:23.797 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And trust with all your heart

01:04:23.797 --> 01:04:25.799 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that if you have faith,

01:04:25.799 --> 01:04:29.136 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
maintain your faith, and walk by faith,

01:04:29.136 --> 01:04:31.805 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
you definitely will see

01:04:31.805 --> 01:04:36.810 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
all of Jehovah’s promises fulfilled.

